msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:34
msgid ""
"fix #1190: ``deprecated_call()`` now works when the deprecated function has "
"been already called by another test in the same module. Thanks Mikhail "
"Chernykh for the report and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:39
msgid ""
"fix #1198: ``--pastebin`` option now works on Python 3. Thanks Mehdy "
"Khoshnoody for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:42
msgid ""
"fix #1219: ``--pastebin`` now works correctly when captured output contains "
"non-ascii characters. Thanks Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:45
msgid ""
"fix #1204: another error when collecting with a nasty __getattr__(). Thanks "
"Freya Bruhin for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:48
msgid ""
"fix the summary printed when no tests did run. Thanks Freya Bruhin for the "
"PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.8.4.rst:51
msgid ""
"a number of documentation modernizations wrt good practices. Thanks Bruno "
"Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""
